{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I played a couple of games in Hakoah at Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we came to a friendly game, to Sydney, in about six, seven weeks after my Melbourne staying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In those days, the Australian Federation formed and broke away from the Association, which meant that Hakoah could get me from Melbourne without any clearance whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because Melbourne was-- and still is-- one section of the Australian Soccer Association.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Federation formed by Hakoah with all the top teams joined them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to play Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a Hakoah member for about three years, four years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Hakoah helped me tremendously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Melbourne, I had a job as a-- as a laborer in an Abattoir.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Hakoah, I was an electric plater for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my English started picking up, I got a job from a tremendously nice gentleman who died next to me on the dancing floor in a Hakoah club.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was a company representative for a printing firm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in 1960, I bought a taxicab because I made enough money from football to buy a cab.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a cabbie from 1960 to '71, which made me even more street wise than I was before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a tremendous experience in 10 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in that 10 years, I played football for about three or four years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the rest of them, I retired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I became a coach of Auburn, the football club, which was top division then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in 1971, my cab was involved in an accident where three people died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I just couldn't do it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I sold my taxicab.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was in the night time, and my night driver had injury, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They told me he died.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
